      "knowledge": "• Explain the correct components of a scientific herbarium label (organism name, date, location, collector, habitat notes)\n• Describe the role and significance of the National Museums of Kenya (NMK) herbarium in plant taxonomy and conservation\n• Explain how properly preserved and labelled herbarium specimens serve as long-term scientific records of biodiversity",
      "skills": "• Mount pressed plant specimens onto herbarium sheets using correct technique and produce accurate, complete scientific labels\n• Evaluate how their own school-environment collection contributes evidence about local plant biodiversity",
