      "purposeInStoryline": "This penultimate lesson is the culminating evidence-gathering and synthesis moment: teams bring together everything collected and learned across Lessons 1–6, compile their project portfolios, and revise their initial explanatory models — transforming novice observations into scientifically reasoned accounts of how preservation defeats decomposition.",
